# ── Model artifacts (large & regenerable) ───────────────────────────────────
# Serialized .pkl artifacts total ~1.1G and individual files exceed GitHub's
# 100MB per-file limit (e.g. explainer.pkl ~590MB). Regenerate with
# `python -m src.train`, or distribute via Git LFS / a release attachment.
models/
models_backup/
models_old_41/
!models/
!models/*.pkl

# ── Migration / scratch backups ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.migration_backup/

# ── Logs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log

# ── Large datasets (optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# The 100-disease dataset is ~44MB. Uncomment to keep it out of git and
# distribute it separately if you prefer a lean repo.
# Diseases_and_Symptoms_dataset.csv

